.TH SHELL_NAME 1 "v1.0" "August 2025" "Simple Shell Manual"


.SH NAME
shell_name


.SH DESCRIPTION
shell_name is a simple shell that can execute commands, handle signals and search for executables in the PATH


.SH FEATURES
- Display a prompt (#cisfun$) and wait for user input
- Search PATH for commands
- Execute simple commands with arguments (e.g. ls -l)
- Prevent calling fork() if a command does not exist
- Properly handle Ctrl-C (SIGINT)


